'''João Paulo Moreira Fernandes''' ({{IPA|pt|ʒu.ˈɐ̃w ˈpaw.lu mu.ˈɾej.ɾɐ fɨɾ.ˈnɐ̃.dɨʃ|lang}}; born 26 May 1998), commonly known as '''João Paulo''', is a Cape Verdean professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder (association football)|midfielder]] or a [[left-back]] for [[Liga I]] club [[FCSB]] and the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Club career==
In June 2025, the player moved to [[ASC Oțelul Galați|Oțelul Galați]] from [[Liga I]], signing a two-year contract.<ref>{{cite news |title=Bem-vindo, Joao Paulo! |trans-title=Welcome, Joao Paulo! |url=https://ascotelul.ro/bem-vindo-joao-paulo/ |work=ascotelul.ro |date=30 June 2025 |access-date=30 June 2025 |language=Romanian}}</ref>

==International career==
Fernandes was called up to the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] for a pair of friendlies in June 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://inforpress.cv/football-newcomers-sixten-mohlin-joao-correia-rely-cabral-and-alexis-goncalves-are-new-in-bubistas-call-up/|title=Football: Newcomers Sixten Mohlin, João Correia, Rely Cabral and Alexis Gonçalves are new in Bubista's call-up &#124; INFORPRESS|date=27 May 2021|access-date=9 June 2021|archive-date=30 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130204751/https://inforpress.cv/football-newcomers-sixten-mohlin-joao-correia-rely-cabral-and-alexis-goncalves-are-new-in-bubistas-call-up/|url-status=dead}}</ref> He debuted with the Cape Verde national team in a friendly 2–0 loss to [[Senegal national football team|Senegal]] on 8 June 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://globalsportsarchive.com/match/soccer/2021-06-08/senegal-vs-cape-verde-islands/2376236/|title=Match Report of Senegal vs Cape Verde Islands – 2021-06-08 – FIFA Friendlies – Global Sports Archive|website=globalsportsarchive.com}}</ref>

